views.markdown: If you need help with "Legacy Scenic", you can contact thenatis, the developer, via e-mail.
Willbraff  is the maintainer of the package "Legacy Scenic". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "wbraffman's repo" repo, William Braffman.
